  "texts": [
    "To determine the optimal pool size, K value, and T value for the dataset implementing this method, a larger range of experimental research is required.",
    "When applied to transfer learning models, it has been observed that the T-Max-Avg method achieves more successful results on ChestX, ResNet50, and DenseNet121 models compared to traditional pooling methods.",
    "Afterwards, by means of cross-ensemble techniques, the model is further improved to achieve higher accuracy and minimize errors.",
    "The T-Max-Avg method is a combination of the Avg-TopK pooling method and the maximum pooling method.",
    "Its design aims to eliminate the drawbacks of traditional pooling methods."
